      <title>Renaud-Chatelain：信用利差过紧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-12/credit-spreads-too-tight-renaud-chatelain-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Pictet Wealth Management 固定收益策略师 Laureline Renaud-Chatelain 更青睐投资级公司债券，而非高收益债券，因为利差太窄。她还表示，国债是平衡投资组合的良好对冲工具。她在“开盘交易”节目中与彭博社的 Guy Johnson 和 Anna Edwards 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-12/credit-spreads-too-tight-renaud-chatelain-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 16:58:11 GMT</pubDate>
